# Magnet Lines

Pure DOM CSS grid of line elements that rotate to point toward the cursor via CSS custom property, creating a magnetic field visualization with zero external dependencies.

## Use when
- Adding a subtle interactive field effect to a dark landing page background.
- Decorating a section with a minimal geometric cursor-reactive element.
- Creating a playful, lightweight interactive demo with no library overhead.

## Stack
- Framework: react
- Libraries: (none)

